Package: SeuratVizHelper
Title: Enhanced Visualization Tools for Seurat Single-Cell Analysis
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Ayumu", "Okumura", , "okumura-ayumu958@g.ecc.u-tokyo.ac.jp", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides Scanpy-style stacked violin plots and other publication-ready 
    visualizations for Seurat single-cell RNA-seq analysis. Includes dendrogram-based 
    cluster ordering and flexible plotting options.
